  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3503116">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3503116/" class="title-link">不读钱先生，人生一大憾事</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3503116"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/fsh267/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u33797818-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fsh267/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">小恒</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-04"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-04 09:04:49</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3503116_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                       读完了，突然发现要摘抄的东西实在太多，索性不写了。精炼文字，睿智篇章，句句语录！！！      这里串用影评的一句话：你可以看三部普通的作品，然后慢慢忘掉，也可以花同样的时间读三遍钱先生，然后喜欢上他，慢慢受益终生。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3503116_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3503116_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





