        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44720122/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44720122/" class="">第20页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/146647516/" class=" " title="翊吁嚱">翊吁嚱</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44720122">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">人生的刺，就在这里，留恋着不肯快走的，偏是你所不留恋的东西。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-06-08 23:55</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>人生的刺，就在这里，留恋着不肯快走的，偏是你所不留恋的东西。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

